Like a shadow in these empty hands

1258
01:27:33,479 --> 01:27:36,396
What we got

1259
01:27:36,896 --> 01:27:39,437
Isn't what we had imagined

1260
01:27:39,937 --> 01:27:46,312
Return those moments to me

1261
01:27:46,854 --> 01:27:52,521
I call out to you right now

1262
01:27:53,521 --> 01:28:00,271
The world we existed together in

1263
01:28:00,646 --> 01:28:06,854
Can someone return that world to me?

1264
01:28:08,021 --> 01:28:10,729
What I got

1265
